title: EYL #202 Jalen Rose on NIL Rule, Fab 5, His Charter School, & Broadcasting
itunes:title: EYL #202 Jalen Rose on NIL Rule, Fab 5, His Charter School, & Broadcasting
description:
In this episode we sat down with the legendary Jalen Rose to talk about the NCAA's controversial NIL rule, the Fab Five's cultural impact, and the world of sports broadcasting. 

We also spoke about his charter school in Detroit, and fundraising. #jalenrose #nil #earnyourleisure
